strings: <voice_0x010009E5><se_low>*: What on earth are you two rascals up to now? Stop it at once!

<voice_0x010009E6><se_low>*: Where are your manners!?
That's no way to welcome travellers!
<voice_0x010009E9><se_low>*: Didn't Miss Jessica ask you to run an errand for her? And here you are playing around!

<voice_0x010009EB><se_low>*: You'd better run along before Jessica
finds out!

<voice_0x010009ED><se_low>*: I'm so sorry.
They don't mean any harm.
<voice_0x010009EE><se_low>*: It's just that our village has been through a lot lately. Ask around for yourselves. You'll see.

<voice_0x010009EF><se_low>*: There's nothing wrong with the place, mind. It's a lovely village, really.
Make yourselves at home.
